     H            Y.
     F** EDTR04B **********************************************************
     F*  UTILITY- EDIT NUM FOR CUSTOMER CODE (EX. 291 -->0291)            *
     F*-------------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.                                                     *
     F*                    CALL 'EDTR04B'
     F*                    PARM           $IN     4
     F*                    PARM           $OUT    4
     F*   IN  $IN   :  4A INPUT                                           *
     F*   OUT $OUT  :  4A OUTPUT                                          *
     F*   EX.                                                             *
     F*  '291' --> '0291'                                                 *
     F*********************************************************************
     E                    IN          4  1
     F******************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $IN     4
     C                     PARM           $OUT    4
      *
     C                     MOVEL'0000'    $OUT
     C                     MOVE $IN       LAST1   1
     C                     MOVE $IN       LAST2   2
     C                     MOVE $IN       LAST3   3
     C                     MOVE $IN       LAST4   4
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           LAST4     WHEQ *BLANK
     C           LAST3     WHEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL$IN       LTR1    1
     C                     MOVE LTR1      $OUT
     C           LAST2     WHEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL$IN       LTR2    2
     C                     MOVE LTR2      $OUT
     C           LAST1     WHEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL$IN       LTR3    3
     C                     MOVE LTR3      $OUT
     C                     OTHER
     C                     MOVEL$IN       $OUT
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
